ings in Jakarta|tallest building]] in Jakarta, as well as Indonesia<ref name=\":0\">{{cite news|title=Eight tallest buildings in Jakarta: Skyscraper Center|last=|first=|date=|newspaper=The Jakarta Post}}</ref>.\n\nThe tower is a 308 meter tall<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://travel.detik.com/travel-news/d-3280728/wow-ini-dia-hotel-tertinggi-se-indonesia-the-westin-jakarta|title=Wow! Ini Dia Hotel Tertinggi Se-Indonesia: The Westin Jakarta|last=Ramadhanny|first=Fitraya|website=detikTravel|language=id|access-date=2019-06-13}}</ref> [[skyscraper]] (289 m excluding the tip)<ref name=\":0\" /> with 69 floors above and 4 floors below the ground. The land area of the tower development is 1.6 hectares. It has a parking lot for over 1,100 vehicles. At present, the tower is the [[List of tallest buildings in Indonesia|tallest building in Indonesia]] and [[List of tallest buildings in the world|74th tallest building in the world]]. The tower is a mixed office and hotel building. Construction of the tower was started in 2011. The tower was topped off in 2015 and opened on August 2016.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://properti.kompas.com/read/2016/08/05/090739521/gedung.tertinggi.di.indonesia.resmi.dibuka.26.agustus.2016|title=Gedung Tertinggi di Indonesia Resmi Dibuka 26 Agustus 2016}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web |title=Transformation Starts Here |url=https://www.henshinjakarta.com/ |website=Henshin |accessdate=30 December 2018}}</ref>\n\nGama Tower is a luxury office tower which applies [[green building]] concepts and development. [[Westin Hotel]] occupies the top 20 floors of the tower, between the 50th and 69th floors. 360 degree views of Jakarta can be observed from the restaurant at the 51st floor. '''Henshin''' operates a club and lounge at the 67th floor as well as restaurant at 68th and 69th floor, the topmost floor of the tower.  A function hall is also located within the 69th floor.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://travel.detik.com/travel-news/3280728/wow-ini-dia-hotel-tertinggi-se-indonesia-the-westin-jakarta|title=Wow! This is the Highest Hotel in Indonesia: The Westin Jakarta}}</ref> The rest of the floors are executive office spaces.\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Jakarta|Indonesia|Architecture}}\n* [[List of tallest buildings in Jakarta]]\n* [[List of tallest buildings in Indonesia]]\n* [[List of tallest buildings in Southeast Asia]]\n\n==External links==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20181003175747/http://gamaland.co.id/project.html Gama Tower]\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n[[Category:Towers in Indonesia]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Jakarta]]\n[[Category:Skyscrapers in Jakarta]]\n[[Category:Post-independence architecture of Indonesia]]\n[[Category:Skyscraper office buildings in Indonesia]]\n[[Category:Skyscraper hotels]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures completed in 2015]]\n", "text_old": "{{coord|-6.224153|106.833731|region:ID_type:landmark_scale:3700|display=title}}\n{{Infobox building\n| name = Gama Tower\n| native_name = \n| image = Gama Tower, Jakarta.jpg\n| image_size = 200px\n| start_date = 2011\n| completion_date = 2015\n| building_type = Office and hotel\n| location = [[Jakarta]], [[Indonesia]]\n| address = Kav-C22, [[Jalan H R Rasuna Said]], [[South Jakarta]]\n| cost = \n| architectural = {{convert|288.6|m|abbr=on}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://skyscrapercenter.com/building/cemindo-tower/17562 |title=Gama Tower |publisher=The Skyscraper Center |date=2014-08-26 |accessdate=2016-09-07}}</ref>\n| tip = {{convert|310|m|abbr=on}} <ref name=\"thejakartapost1\"/>\n| top_floor = {{convert|288.6|m|abbr=on}}\n| observatory = \n| floor_count = 62 (top floor designated as 69, due to number skippings)\n| floor_area = 163,466 m\u00b2 / 1,759,533 ft\u00b2\n| elevator_count = 33, made by [[Schindler]]\n| architect = PT Sekawan Design Inc. Architect\n| structural_engineer = Taylor Thomson Whitting\n| owner = PT Gamaland\n| developer = Cushman & Wakefield\n| main_contractor = PT Tatamulia Nusantara Indah\n| references = \n| former_names = Cemindo Tower, Rasuna Tower\n}}\n\n[[File:Gama_Tower_Jakarta_Sunset.jpg|thumb|left|300px|Gama Tower and neighboring buildings at Sunset]]\n\n'''Gama Tower''' (formerly known as ''Cemindo Tower'') is a skyscraper located at [[Jalan H R Rasuna Said]], [[South Jakarta]], [[Indonesia]]. It was also known as ''Rasuna Tower'' and ''Cemindo Tower'' during construction period, but finally named as ''Gama Tower''.<ref name=\"thejakartapost1\">{{cite web|author=The Jakarta Post |url=http://www.thejakartapost.com/travel/2016/08/23/jakartas-tallest-hotel-set-to-attract-business-travelers.html |title=Jakarta's tallest hotel set to attract business travelers |publisher=The Jakarta Post |date=2016-08-23 |accessdate=2016-09-07}}</ref> As of 2018, it is the [[List of tallest buildings in Jakarta|tallest building]] in Jakarta, as well as Indonesia<ref name=\":0\">{{cite news|title=Eight tallest buildings in Jakarta: Skyscraper Center|last=|first=|date=|newspaper=The Jakarta Post}}</ref>.\n\nThe tower is a 308 meter tall<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://travel.detik.com/travel-news/d-3280728/wow-ini-dia-hotel-tertinggi-se-indonesia-the-westin-jakarta|title=Wow! Ini Dia Hotel Tertinggi Se-Indonesia: The Westin Jakarta|last=Ramadhanny|first=Fitraya|website=detikTravel|language=id|access-date=2019-06-13}}</ref> [[skyscraper]] (289 m excluding the tip)<ref name=\":0\" /> with 69 floors above and 4 floors below the ground. The land area of the tower development is 1.6 hectares. It has a parking lot for over 1,100 vehicles. At present, the tower is the [[List of tallest buildings in Indonesia|tallest building in Indonesia]] and [[List of tallest buildings in the world|74th tallest building in the world]]. The tower is a mixed office and hotel building. Construction of the tower was started in 2011. The tower was topped off in 2015 and opened on August 2016.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://properti.kompas.com/read/2016/08/05/090739521/gedung.tertinggi.di.indonesia.resmi.dibuka.26.agustus.2016|title=Gedung Tertinggi di Indonesia Resmi Dibuka 26 Agustus 2016}}</ref> <ref>{{cite web |title=Transformation Starts Here |url=https://www.henshinjakarta.com/ |website=Henshin |accessdate=30 December 2018}}</ref>\n\nGama Tower is a luxury office tower which applies [[green building]] concepts and development. [[Westin Hotel]] occupies the top 20 floors of the tower, between the 50th and 69th floors. 360 degree views of Jakarta can be observed from the restaurant at the 51st floor. '''Henshin''' operates a club and lounge at the 67th floor as well as restaurant at 68th and 69th floor, the topmost floor of the tower.  A function hall is also located within the 69th floor.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://travel.detik.com/travel-news/3280728/wow-ini-dia-hotel-tertinggi-se-indonesia-the-westin-jakarta|title=Wow! This is the Highest Hotel in Indonesia: The Westin Jakarta}}</ref> The rest of the floors are executive office spaces.\n\n==See also==\n{{Portal|Jakarta|Indonesia|Architecture}}\n* [[List of tallest buildings in Jakarta]]\n* [[List of tallest buildings in Indonesia]]\n* [[List of tallest buildings in Southeast Asia]]\n\n==External links==\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20181003175747/http://gamaland.co.id/project.html Gama Tower]\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n[[Category:Towers in Indonesia]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures in Jakarta]]\n[[Category:Skyscrapers in Jakarta]]\n[[Category:Post-independence architecture of Indonesia]]\n[[Category:Skyscraper office buildings in Indonesia]]\n[[Category:Skyscraper hotels]]\n[[Category:Buildings and structures completed in 2015]]\n", "name_user": "NL2520", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gama_Tower"}
