a.htm|title=St. Benedict of Aniane. In the Catholic Encyclopedia.|last=Kirsch|first=J.P.|date=1907|website=www.newadvent.org|publisher=Robert Appleton Company|url-status=live|archive-url=|archive-date=|access-date=2020-04-03|transcription=}}</ref>||c.745-750||&nbsp;France||821||&nbsp;Germany||[[Bishop of Bourges]]\n|-\n|[[Peter of Atroa]]||773||&nbsp;||837||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Frederick of Utrecht|Frederick]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||838||&nbsp;||[[Archdiocese of Utrecht (695\u20131580)|Bishop of Utrecht]]\n|-\n|[[Gunioc]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||838||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Nicetas of Constantinople]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||838||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Agobard]], Archbishop of Lyons||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||840||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Ansovinus]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||840||&nbsp;||[[Bishop of Camerino]]\n|-\n|[[Arnulf of Eynesbury|Arnulf]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||840||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Bolcan]] (Olcan of Kilmayle)||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||840||&nbsp;||[[Bishop of Derban]]\n|-\n|Paul||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||840||&nbsp;||[[Bishop of Prusa]]\n|-\n|[Theophylact||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||840||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Aldericus]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||841||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Theodore and Theophanes]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||841||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Bernard]] (Barnard)||778||&nbsp;||842||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Ardo Smaragdus]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||843||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Gohardus]] and Companions||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||843||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|Paulinus||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||843||&nbsp;||[[Bishop of Capua]]\n|-\n|[[Hildeman]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||844||&nbsp;||[[Bishop of Beauvais]]\n|-\n|[[Benedict of Macerac]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||845||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|Fulk||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||845||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Theophylact of Nicomedia|Theophylact]] (Theophilus)||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||845||&nbsp;||[[Bishop of Nicomedia]]\n|-\n|[[Joannicus]]||754||&nbsp;||846||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Deochar]] (Gottlieb, Theutger)||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||847||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Methodius I]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||847||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Martyrs of Amorion]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||848||&nbsp;||\n|-\n|[[Adalgis]]||&nbsp;||&nbsp;||850||&nbsp;||[[Bishop of Novara]]\n|-\n|[[Badulfus]]||&nbsp;|